.step
  h2 Type coercion
  p.
    Stylus performs type coercion when appropriate, and
    supports all of the unit types you've come to know and love.
  textarea.stylus
    body
      foo: foo + bar
      foo: 'foo ' + bar
      foo: 'foo ' + 'bar'
      foo: 'foo ' + 5px
      foo: 2s - 500ms
      foo: 5000ms == 5s
      foo: 50deg
